{"tid":2490972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵朗屏站40歲男子殘廁暴斃　職員關站前巡查發現","createTime":"2021-04-16T03:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:40:30.000Z","uid":115598,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"232655f5ae142a38de12572df30978ffb56285f4","tid":2490972,"uid":115598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"今日凌晨約1時，警員接獲朗屏站的職員報案，指在關站巡查時發現一名男子懷疑在一個傷殘廁所內暈倒。救護員接報到場，事主當場被證實死亡。警方到場調查，初步得悉死者40歲姓張，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n警員事後召食環署仵工到場，將遺體舁送殮房，案件列作「屍體發現」跟進。<br />\n<br />\n死神來了...40真係好後生"},{"pid":"d17902e906928b602fe5f7c65231e771cd86576d","tid":2490972,"uid":46896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"有冇打4hing ？"},{"pid":"84a9e4eb4245c84827fc15d3599055c422b89b2a","tid":2490972,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6011278fd8e3e64653f20f13c433279a877c3a","tid":2490972,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"冇食早餐？"},{"pid":"63d7d608eaa6ecf2555f72b99d1a52355e24309d","tid":2490972,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"又Four兄？"},{"pid":"ac62db679cf82b06bfba6d3d6d5a9be4d76e9541","tid":2490972,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"科興？"},{"pid":"6c719bf4d8529461c06dc99dcc4d98b463c5ce94","tid":2490972,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"香港唔少公司迫員工打針<br />\n因為中共放風唔認伏必泰 <br />\n通常打工仔迫住打都係打科興"},{"pid":"597a7607959fe6b6bf09ac0764f3a348fafe4b0c","tid":2490972,"uid":174060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXBvrvLdPBvtx2TcpTjU5PRUk9vj2mGwYkv8dQfD2ne1K?filename=A701REy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"